cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI 

This paper deals with modeling language and translations between languages, which falls under the sub-category of natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also uses mathematical and computational methods to formalize the notion of a lexicon and dictionary of meanings, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of monoidal categories also suggests a focus on mathematical foundations (cs.DS) and possibly information theory (cs.SI).
